paragraphs.text:
%spark

import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
 

var cveApi = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("https://api-us-west-2.srcclr.com/catalog/search?q=language%3Ajava%20type%3Avulnerability"), Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

val pageSizeDf = sqlContext.read.json(cveApi).select("metadata.pageSize").toDF()

val pageSize = pageSizeDf.selectExpr("cast(pageSize as int) as pageSize").map( x => x.getInt(0)).first()

for (i <- 2 to pageSize) {
   val eachApi = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("https://api-us-west-2.srcclr.com/catalog/search?q=language%3Ajava%20type%3Avulnerability&page="+i), Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))
   cveApi = eachApi.union(cveApi)
}


val cveApiJson = sqlContext.read.json(cveApi).toDF()

paragraphs.title: 컨텐츠 및 라이브러리 추출
paragraphs.text:
%spark

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.{udf, explode}
val zip = udf((xs: Seq[String], ys: Seq[String]) => xs.zip(ys))

val contents = cveApiJson.select(explode($"contents").as("contents"))

val df = contents.select($"contents.model.id", $"contents._severity", $"contents.model.title",$"contents.model.disclosureDate", $"contents.model.cveYear", $"contents.model.cveDigits", $"artifact.coordTwo",$"artifact.versionRanges.updateToVersion", $"artifact.versionRanges.versionRange",explode($"contents.model.artifactComponents").as("artifact"))


val result = df.withColumn("vars", explode(zip($"versionRange", $"updateToVersion"))).select(
   $"id", $"_severity", $"title", $"cveYear", $"cveDigits", $"coordTwo", $"vars._1".alias("versionRange"), $"vars._2".alias("updateToVersion"), $"disclosureDate") 
   
result.show()

paragraphs.title: CVE(Common Vulnerabilities and Exposure) JAVA
paragraphs.text:
%sql

SELECT _severity, CASE
    WHEN _severity < 4 THEN "low"
    WHEN _severity < 7 THEN "medium"
    WHEN _severity <= 10 THEN "high"
END as risk, title, CONCAT("CVE","-",cveYear,"-",cveDigits) cve, coordTwo as artifact,  versionRange as affectsVersion, updateToVersion, timestamp as disclosureDate
FROM cveTable
